    "contextBuilder": {
        "description": "Character sheet _prepareContext should build ctx.ritualPanel for BC actors. Only the Daemonic Mastery rating is persisted (sys.ritualMastery); the per-ritual template id, base target, modifier stack, and rolled outcome are all dialog-scoped state on the action handler — no per-sheet ephemeral slot is needed. Pseudocode:",
        "pseudocode": [
            "if (this.actor._gameSystemId === 'bc') {",
            "  ctx.ritualPanel = {",
            "    ritualMastery: this.actor.system.ritualMastery ?? 0,",
            "  };",
            "}",
            "The Perform Ritual button (data-action=\"bcPerformRitual\") opens the dialog itself; the orchestrator only needs to register bcPerformRitual into DEFAULT_OPTIONS.actions and include the panel partial inside the isBC gate in tab-overview.hbs."
        ]
    }
